<title>USA: British Aerospace to buy rest of Reflectone.</title>
<headline>British Aerospace to buy rest of Reflectone.</headline>
<dateline>TAMPA 1997-02-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>British Aerospace Holdings Inc and Reflectone Inc said on Thursday that they have signed a merger agreement in which British Aerospace will buy the remaining common stock of Reflectone at $24 per share.</p>
<p>British Aerospace currently owns 48 percent of Reflectone's outstanding common stock.</p>
<p>Reflectone designs and manufactures flight simulators, weapons systems trainers, tactical air defense trainers, maintenance trainers, part-task trainers and other training devices for the U.S. Government, commercial and international customers.</p>
